In spite of the fact that the Industry Sector has received priority ranking of 5, it is considered as the third priority sector due to the following reasons;
* Both energy and industry sectors depend primarily on fossil fuels and the technologies in these two sectors are closely related. Hence, it is mutually beneficial to consider industry sector overthe waste sector.
* Some barriers and measures of energy and industry sectors are very similar or common. This would be an advantage for diffusion of technologies within both the sectors.
